1 accomplishments; and
2 WHEREAS, Dr. Savoie's legacy will endure not only through the institutions he
3 strengthened and the reforms he championed, but also through the countless lives he
4 influenced and the enduring belief that education remains one of the most powerful forces
5 for opportunity, progress, and public good.
6 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
7 does hereby commend Dr. E. Joseph Savoie on the occasion of his retirement for his
8 exemplary and selfless public service, visionary leadership, and extraordinary contributions
9 to higher education in Louisiana spanning nearly five decades; does hereby express profound
10 gratitude for his enduring commitment to the students, institutions, and residents of this
11 state; and does hereby extend sincerest wishes for continued happiness, health, and success
12 in all of his future endeavors.
13 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Dr.
14 E. Joseph Savoie.
